name: The Beekman, A Thompson Hotel
description: Nestled in the epicenter of Lower Manhattans vibrant new downtown lies New Yorks last hidden architectural treasure - The Beekman a Thompson Hotel. One of Manhattans first skyscrapers the heart of this iconic building is its extraordinary nine-story Victorian atrium and majestic pyramidal skylight. Originally the site played host to many milestones including New Yorks debut of Shakespeares Hamlet and the famed Clinton Hall a library where writers such as Edgar Allen Poe honed their craft

name: Refinery Hotel
description: Situated in Manhattan, Refinery Hotel offers modern accommodation with superior amenities. It is located a brief walk from Empire State Building, Times Square and the New York Public Library. Guests can make the most of the sun on the terrace or have a drink at the bar. Free Wi-Fi access is available. The rooms are air conditioned and feature an iPod docking station, a mini bar and a private bathroom. They all offer a flat-screen TV, a seating area and an in-room safe. On-site dining options include a restaurant, which is a convenient spot to enjoy a meal. Guests can also try one of the various bars and restaurants in the area. New York City's popular tourist spots are within close proximity to Refinery Hotel, with Bryant Park only a five-minute stroll away. Guests can also visit Madison Square Garden and Rockefeller Center

name: Harlem Lodge
description: Located within 1.6 mi of Columbia University and 2.2 mi of Metropolitan Museum of Art in New York, Harlem Lodge provides accommodations with free WiFi and flat-screen TV. All units are air conditioned and include a seating and/or dining area. Yankee Stadium is 2.4 mi from the apartment, while Strawberry Fields is 3.1 mi away. The nearest airport is LaGuardia Airport, 4.3 mi from Harlem Lodge

name: The Harlem Cascades
description: Located 1.7 mi from Columbia University in New York, The Harlem Cascades provides accommodations with air conditioning and free WiFi. The apartment offers a seating area with a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a hairdryer, free toiletries and shower. Yankee Stadium is 2.1 mi from The Harlem Cascades, while Metropolitan Museum of Art is 2.6 mi away. The nearest airport is LaGuardia Airport, 4.3 mi from the accommodations

name: NH Collection New York Madison Avenue
description: The NH Collection New York Madison Avenue in New York is situated in the heart of the city, and has been completely refurbished in 2020. Guests of the NH Collection New York Madison Avenue hotel are within easy walking distance of major Manhattan attractions. Take in the hustle and bustle of Times Square, then cap off your day with a trip to the top of the Empire State Building. For legendary shopping, visit Madison Avenue, Fifth Avenue, and Grand Central Terminal. Art enthusiasts can access priceless works of art at the MoMA within minutes, while the nearby Bryant Park offers a scenic spot for a cup of coffee. For the business traveler, the NH Collection New York Madison Avenue in New York City provides sophisticated meeting facilities that comfortably host events for groups of up to 30. A gym, bar and tearoom are also open onsite, giving you the perfect place to dine, unwind and stay in shape in the city that never sleeps

name: The Nomad Suites & Apartments
description: With a stay at The Nomad Suites & Apartments, you'll be centrally located in New York, steps from 5th Avenue and 4 minutes by foot from Empire State Building. Featured amenities include a 24-hour front desk, luggage storage, and laundry facilities. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite
